                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18321129-127-off711 t18321129-127-cd712"></join>, 6 brushes, value 14s. 6d., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18321129-127-victim1208" type="victimName">
