                     <interp inst="t18321129-127-person1212" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am foreman to Mr. Kent. This brush I can swear to - the prisoner's brother was not employed by us; the prisoner has hitherto borne a good character.</p>
